fb8/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2308x1212+0+163/resize/1200x630!/quality/85/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F44%2F0a%2Fd32213ec496297a44590d1a3fae2%2Fabsoluteblack-aether-carbon-ultra-light-tubeless-valves-1.jpeg&amp;na.image_optimisation=0\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<img src=\"https://assets.newatlas.com/dims4/default/cd41fb8/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2308x1212+0+163/resize/1200x630!/quality/85/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F44%2F0a%2Fd32213ec496297a44590d1a3fae2%2Fabsoluteblack-aether-carbon-ultra-light-tubeless-valves-1.jpeg&amp;na.image_optimisation=0\" style=\"width:100%;max-height:300px;object-fit:cover;\" />\n<p><img alt=\"The Aether is a coreless Presta valve stem designed for use on tubeless road, gravel and mountain bike tires\" src=\"https://assets.newatlas.com/dims4/default/cbaa7c1/2147483647/strip/true/crop/2308x1538+0+0/resize/1440x960!/format/webp/quality/85/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fnewatlas-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2F44%2F0a%2Fd32213ec496297a44590d1a3fae2%2Fabsoluteblack-aether-carbon-ultra-light-tubeless-valves-1.jpeg\" /><p>Presta valves are one of those things that a lot of serious cyclists use, but perhaps secretly hate. Well, those folks might have a much more loving relationship with the Aether valve stem, which does away with a traditional Presta valve's problematic core.</p><p><a href=\"https://newatlas.com/bicycles/absoluteblack-aether-coreless-valve-stem/\">Continue Reading</a></p><p><b>Category:</b> <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/bicycles/\">Bicycles</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/transport/\">Transport</a></p><p><b>Tags:</b> <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/tires/\" rel=\"tag\">Tires</a>, <a href=\"https://newatlas.com/tag/cycling/\" rel=\"tag\">Cycling</a></p>",
